  "prompt": "Where can I find device art generators for Samsung S5?",
  "response": "There are several online resources and tools where you can find device art generators for the Samsung Galaxy S5:\n\n1. Android Device Art Generator\n- Official Google website\n- Allows you to add screenshots to device frames\n- Free and easy to use\n\n2. Placeit\n- Online design tool with device mockups\n- Offers various templates for Samsung S5\n- Some features require paid subscription\n\n3. MockUPhone\n- Free online tool\n- Provides device frames for multiple smartphones\n- Simple interface for quick mockups\n\n4. Canva\n- Graphic design platform\n- Has device mockup templates\n- Free and paid options available\n\n5. Adobe Photoshop\n- Professional design software\n- Requires manual frame creation or downloading templates\n- Offers most customization options\n\n6. GitHub repositories\n- Some developers share device art generator scripts\n- Free and customizable options\n\nTips:\n- Check image resolution and quality\n- Compare different generators\n- Some tools offer free and premium features\n- Download high-quality PNG or PSD files\n\nMost of these resources offer quick and easy ways to create professional-looking device art for your Samsung S5.",
